    },
    {
      "key": "0a7f3c26-be45-4f5f-b861-e54e263f33f7",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "The unit assessment project assesses proficiency in the knowledge and skills developed in this unit. It is completed in three class periods to plan and create the program, including choosing and uploading images and creating a new image filter or image manipulation algorithm. Students participate in planning and feedback activities to solve problems, reinforce software development practices and self-image as software engineers, and improve their programs.\n\nIf there is not enough time for the three-day project, a one-day option achieves the targeted learning objectives and goals. If using this option, refer to the [**Abstract Data Art Project 1-Day Lesson Plan**](https://studio.code.org/s/csa5-2023/lessons/14). While the one-day option covers the learning objectives and goals, it shortens planning and reflection time. Consider this tradeoff when deciding which version to use."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "0a7f3c26-be45-4f5f-b861-e54e263f33f7",
        "lesson_activity.key": "8615a819-1205-4790-81fe-3f44880d78b4"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "0afec3b9-ca84-466c-bef7-5cfa796b7eab",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "We have seen some examples of image filters, collages, and animations throughout the unit. People often use images and image filters are often used in collages and animations to portray a story about personal experiences or interests.",
        "duration": "10",
        "name": "Warm Up",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "0afec3b9-ca84-466c-bef7-5cfa796b7eab",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "7771de96-3c21-4fd5-8794-e0adb334d021",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Show examples of different types of personal narratives.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *What does this make you wonder about how you could create a collage or animation about your personal experiences or interests?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students share ideas about collages or animations they might make to portray their personal experiences or interests. Students might wonder about how more complex visuals might be created or about the design choices the creators made about their visuals."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "7771de96-3c21-4fd5-8794-e0adb334d021",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "5372d487-e84b-486f-82f4-6ebd02ad22a4",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Over the next few days, you will be developing a program that creates a new image filter and puts the images you chose together in a collage or animation.",
        "duration": "15",
        "name": "Brainstorming and Planning",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "5372d487-e84b-486f-82f4-6ebd02ad22a4",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "48e3e149-e3b7-425e-968c-0c6ec48131a5",
      "position": 4,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Distribute:** Give each student a copy of the Personal Narrative Project Planning Guide.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the project requirements.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to read the rubric on pages 2 and 3.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *What do you notice about the project requirements and rubric? What does success look like for this project?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students share what they notice about the project requirements and rubric and identify the components to implement in their program.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *What barriers do you anticipate to achieving success on this project?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students identify barriers they anticipate and share any questions they have about the project.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "Use the Hold That Thought strategy to allow students to write down their thoughts on paper first. Emphasize that they do not need to write complete sentences – they can write a few words, bullet points, draw a quick sketch, or anything else that will help them gather and recall their thoughts when it is time to share with the class."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "48e3e149-e3b7-425e-968c-0c6ec48131a5",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "875138da-261d-4b59-bded-00e3bf4f2a89",
      "position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "description": "**Do This:** Introduce the steps students will take each day to complete the project:\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Day 1 steps\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Day 2 steps\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Day 3 steps"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "875138da-261d-4b59-bded-00e3bf4f2a89",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "41c17514-29f4-40d4-b7f2-958053a83f83",
      "position": 6,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Before you begin writing your program, you first need to decide what personal experiences or interests you want to portray and how you will visualize these in a collage or animation. You will need to plan how you will organize your program and images, and identify the algorithms you need to develop to create your new image filter.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "41c17514-29f4-40d4-b7f2-958053a83f83",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "0c425e08-7259-4fc4-8789-26d8543d6440",
      "position": 7,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to plan their collage or animation, create UML diagrams for their classes, and identify the algorithms they need to develop on the Personal Narrative Project Planning Guide."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "0c425e08-7259-4fc4-8789-26d8543d6440",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "f6dc3481-3ddb-4a2a-a8a3-a1fde1787202",
      "position": 8,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to Level 1 on Code Studio to develop their Personal Narrative Good Project.",
        "duration": "15",
        "name": "Development",
        "progression_name": "Personal Narrative Project"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "f6dc3481-3ddb-4a2a-a8a3-a1fde1787202",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "8a97edb3-8c71-44a8-9354-a5f7285972c3",
      "position": 9,
      "properties": {
        "description": "This is a good time to commit our code and save our new superclass and subclasses to the Backpack. Anytime we make changes to our programs, it is helpful to commit, or save, our work as a new version in case we need to revert to a previous version.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "8a97edb3-8c71-44a8-9354-a5f7285972c3",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "8da0114b-1139-4ec3-b605-83693d5ee2d1",
      "position": 10,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Play the music clip to cue committing their code and saving their classes to the Backpack.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "Using music to cue transitions helps create routines in the classroom. When students hear cues, they know it is time to transition to a specific activity. Emphasize to students what the music clip means, and be consistent with the use of the music clip to cue the activity.\n\nClick the blue play icon on the slide to play the music cue."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "8da0114b-1139-4ec3-b605-83693d5ee2d1",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "5b65793e-c46f-496d-a8d0-096a6fb1e11a",
      "position": 11,
      "properties": {
        "description": "You made a lot of progress on your project today! Let's take a moment to reflect on what you have accomplished so far and what you need to focus on next.",
        "duration": "5",
        "name": "Wrap Up",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "5b65793e-c46f-496d-a8d0-096a6fb1e11a",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "2cec7997-1f3a-444b-90a2-8d958f23de41",
      "position": 12,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to respond to the Day 1 Reflection prompt on the Personal Narrative Project Planning Guide.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "If time permits, have students share their thoughts and ideas with a neighbor."
          },
          {
            "type": "assessmentOpportunity",
            "markdown": "You can use the Day 1 Reflection as an optional completion assessment."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "2cec7997-1f3a-444b-90a2-8d958f23de41",
        "lesson_activity.key": "25e28683-aae4-44a4-9369-1b65fd4816da"
      }
    },
    {
