    {
      "key": "30787158-b3e5-4785-a6d2-194d6007b967",
      "position": 7,
      "properties": {
        "description": "When we write new code, getting feedback from our peers is helpful to make sure we have met the requirements of the problem efficiently.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "30787158-b3e5-4785-a6d2-194d6007b967",
        "lesson_activity.key": "921a1ef5-c3c8-4aee-8610-e653e4c9b100"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "bc97f2ba-84ec-45be-b737-c8e86d999d32",
      "position": 8,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Click through the animated slide to have students participate in the Code Review Call and Response.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to conduct a code review on their Personal Narrative Project.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "Students may be at different points when it is time for the code review. Emphasize to students that their work does not need to be completed to get feedback. Remind students that the problem-solving and development process is iterative and that receiving feedback from peers while they are working can help give them additional insights, perspectives, and guidance."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "bc97f2ba-84ec-45be-b737-c8e86d999d32",
        "lesson_activity.key": "921a1ef5-c3c8-4aee-8610-e653e4c9b100"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "e11ba408-6ffc-45da-bc3e-bea0bd7308ee",
      "position": 9,
      "properties": {
        "description": "You have a lot of feedback from the code review to help improve your program! Let's review our tasks and priorities and plan updates based on the feedback we received and what we have left to complete.",
        "duration": "10",
        "name": "Revisions, Updates, and Reviews",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "e11ba408-6ffc-45da-bc3e-bea0bd7308ee",
        "lesson_activity.key": "921a1ef5-c3c8-4aee-8610-e653e4c9b100"
      }
    },
    {
