          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "We also have a teacher end-of-unit survey to learn more about how the unit went for you and your students. While students take their survey, please complete [**this end of unit survey for teachers**](https://studio.code.org/form/teacher_end_of_unit_survey?survey_data%5Bunit_number%5D=6) as well. Your feedback is valued and appreciated!"
          }
