    {
      "key": "02408dab-8080-44c7-b792-7c1e37e6f970",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Today, you will complete your first FRQ independently.\n\nStandardized assessments, like the AP exam you will be taking, can be very stressful. Breathing exercises before and even during an exam are an effective way to help us relax and set aside any distractions or negativity to focus on doing our best work. Everyone is different, though, so some exercises are more effective than others for each person. Let's choose a technique to try!",
        "name": "Breathing Exercise",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "02408dab-8080-44c7-b792-7c1e37e6f970",
        "lesson_activity.key": "85f214d5-93bd-45a2-bba6-b79618088047"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "4bc5f79e-3485-49ca-bbf3-f19d4dda8c85",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students participate in one of the breathing exercises."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "4bc5f79e-3485-49ca-bbf3-f19d4dda8c85",
        "lesson_activity.key": "85f214d5-93bd-45a2-bba6-b79618088047"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "3778b21b-6c50-4136-8e50-b17c1c5cc960",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Now that we're ready for this FRQ, let's review the strategies we have practiced for approaching these questions.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "3778b21b-6c50-4136-8e50-b17c1c5cc960",
        "lesson_activity.key": "85f214d5-93bd-45a2-bba6-b79618088047"
      }
    },
