    {
      "key": "d0331203-7b01-4e7a-a7e4-9218d70c1544",
      "position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Congratulations on completing another FRQ! As with any problems we solve in Java, there are multiple approaches to solving an FRQ. Let's look at one solution to today's FRQ.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "d0331203-7b01-4e7a-a7e4-9218d70c1544",
        "lesson_activity.key": "33865c4d-83a6-4130-9abf-c63e524cac49"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "3cb417a8-f04b-432a-85be-427df7403586",
      "position": 6,
      "properties": {
        "description": "**Do This:** Discuss possible solutions to the FRQ. For each solution, walk through each row of the FRQ Scoring Guide and point out how the solution met those requirements. \n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `addTemperatureAction()` accesses all entries of `schedule`\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `addTemperatureAction()`compares the hours and minutes of `TemperatureAction` objects in `schedule` with the hours and minutes of `setting`\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `addTemperatureAction()` adds `TemperatureAction` to `schedule`\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `addTemperatureAction()` overrides the previous setting with the new setting if a time already exists in the schedule\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> On exit, the `schedule` contains all appropriate `TemperatureAction` elements in the correct order\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `removeTemperatureAction()` accesses all entries of `schedule`\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `removeTemperatureAction()` compares instance variables of `TemperatureAction` object in `schedule` and parameter values\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `removeTemperatureAction()` removes from `schedule` all `TemperatureAction` objects which contain a temperature above the given value if the `mode` is `\"cool\"` or below a given value if the `mode` is `\"heat\"`\n* <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> `removeTemperatureAction()` identifies and returns appropriate `boolean` value for all cases"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "3cb417a8-f04b-432a-85be-427df7403586",
        "lesson_activity.key": "33865c4d-83a6-4130-9abf-c63e524cac49"
      }
    },
