      "position": 9,
      "properties": {
        "description": "You now have 25 minutes to complete the free response question. You are responsible for pacing yourself and may proceed freely from Part A to Part B. Show all necessary work and final solutions on the MusicQueue FRQ. Solutions written on scratch paper will not be considered. \n\nGood luck! You may now begin the exam.",
