    {
      "key": "8a80efd8-4dcf-489a-bd37-fe472ceae2f9",
      "position": 10,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students complete the free-response question on the MusicQueue FRQ. On the board, write the start and end times.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "If there is not a visible clock in the room, consider displaying a 25-minute timer.\n\nDuring the AP Exam, students must sit quietly until the allotted testing time has elapsed. If you decide to adhere to this rule closely, encourage students that finish early to:\n* Continue to work on their FRQ.\n* Trace their code to ensure it is correct.\n* Check their solution to ensure it aligns with their pseudocode solution."
          }
