      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Collect the SeatingChart FRQ handout, Java Quick Reference, and scrap paper from each student.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Distribute:** Give each student a copy of the SeatingChart FRQ Scoring Guidelines and one sticky note or scrap piece of paper.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students respond to the prompt on their sticky note or scrap piece of paper.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Play the music clip to cue the Give One, Get One activity and direct students to participate in a Give One, Get One."
